title: Asaayu's Group Marker System
file_description:
[h1]Asaayu's Group Marker System is a completly custom marker system that you can use to easily distinguish members of your group![/h1]
[img] https://i.imgur.com/3NIA8mR.png [/img]
[b]This mod is a client side mod and is not required to be loaded by the server. The mod allows each player to have their own custom name and choose custom icons through the completly custom CTRL - SHIFT - F1 menu!
This mod is plug & play all that is required by clients is to load this mod!

[url=https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/499945342578458636/520547150212628480/Asaayu-GroupMarkers.bikey]Download the key to add to your KEYS folder here![/url]
If you would like a feature added feel free to contact me and request it!

[url=https://twitter.com/AsaayuNZ] [img] https://i.imgur.com/5GVQiqu.png [/img] [/url]

[url=https://steamcommunity.com/id/asaayu/myworkshopfiles/] [img] https://i.imgur.com/u4A7TLR.png [/img] [/url]
